        "name": "SQA acceptance criteria — MRL 5 Class III",
        "description": "The CFD solver must hold a current FDA-recognized SQA certification (ISO 9001:2015 or equivalent). Version-controlled source code with full regression test suite (≥500 test cases, pass rate 100%). Change-control records must be traceable. All simulation scripts must be archived under configuration management with digital checksums. Achieved: ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 certified under ISO 9001; 612-case regression suite passing; all run scripts archived in institutional Git repository with SHA-256 checksums."
