      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 operates under a documented ISO 9001:2015 quality management system. The solver regression suite comprises 612 test cases covering laminar, turbulent, and non-Newtonian blood-analog flows; all pass at the release version used. Simulation input decks, boundary condition files, and post-processing scripts are version-controlled in an institutional GitLab repository. Each committed artifact carries a SHA-256 checksum verified at execution time. Independent audit of the SQA records by the credibility assessment team confirmed compliance with ASME V&V 40 Gradation 4 requirements for Class III device software quality assurance."
