      "rationale": "Use error controls were implemented at multiple levels. The simulation setup — including geometry import, mesh generation parameters, boundary condition specification, turbulence model selection (SST k-ω), and hemolysis model constants — was independently reviewed by a second qualified CFD analyst who had not participated in the original setup. Discrepancies identified in the review (two incorrect inlet turbulence intensity specifications) were corrected prior to the production runs. Boundary conditions were cross-checked line-by-line against the experimental test reports. All mesh quality metrics (maximum skewness 0.42, maximum aspect ratio 8.3) are within ANSYS Fluent recommended limits. These controls satisfy Gradation 3 use error requirements."
